==English==
===Adjective===
'''picayune'''
#[[Petty]], [[trivial]]; of little consequence; small and of little importance; [[picayunish]];
#:'''quotations''':
#:*"It might seem like a '''picayune''' matter, akin to the rivalry in the film "Monty Python's Life of Brian" between the Judean People's Front, the Judean Popular People's Front and the People's Front of Judea." &mdash;''New York Times'', November 17, 2005
#something not worth arguing about.
